*.pyc

# Investment_Research_Dashboard.xlsx is intentionally tracked (not
# ignored): the Streamlit Community Cloud deployment reads it straight
# out of this repo checkout, and git_sync.py pushes it after every
# local sync so the deployed view stays current. Its Excel lock file is
# still transient and never worth tracking.
~$Investment_Research_Dashboard.xlsx
logs/

